well just keep flying for as long as we can or until most of it 
is over 
beryl is the second named storm of the atlantic hurricane 
season the seasons first tropical storm alberto fizzled out 
monday near the canadian coast shortly after noon sunday the 
forecasters had issued a tropical storm warning for maines coast 
from bar harbor to eastport but canceled it in less than six hours 
rain from beryl battered coastal areas monday in louisiana 
