purportedly came from the creature 
the blood and scales headed for a state crime lab for analysis 
apparently are from a dead fish the sheriff said it doesnt 
take an expert to see what they are 
visitors have been pulling off interstate 20 for the past few 
weeks to satisfy their curiosity about the lizard man 
marina watson of the local chamber of commerce said business has 
