hired back but not enough to keep up with the growing demand 
damron said 
there have not been enough applicants and they have not been 
able to produce enough controllers damron said 
ohare airport handles an average of nearly 2200 takeoffs and 
landings a day its 796939 arrivals and departures last year were 
second only to atlantas hartsfield international 
last year ohare handled more than 56 million passengers more 
than any other airport but the airport has been the subject of 
