two months ago in new zealand 
i never believed in this loveatfirstsight thing but im a 
convert now she said 
weve both spent a decade or more in the fast lane weve been 
exposed to the most eligible people in the world i think we 
know ms gibbons a south carolina native said monday in a 
telephone interview with the columbia state from her los angeles 
office 
