would like to be on that stage when i am 80 harrison is a 
charismatic performer and i greatly admire him because he has a 
multitude of tricks up his sleeve 
edward fox who plays the butler crichton said playing rexs 
role requires a lot of stamina he has enormous grit and 
determination 
